@@TJvAnimate
<GROUP TJvAnimate>
Summary
  Enhanced TAnimate control.
Description
  TJvAnimate enhances the VCL's TAnimate control with a HintColor property and various events.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.AboutJVCL
  <INCLUDE JVCL.Main.AboutJVCL.dtx>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.DoMouseEnter
Summary
  Called in response to a mouse enter message.
Description
  DoMouseEnter is called whenever the mouse enter message is received. If OnMouseEnter is assigned
  it will be called, otherwise nothing will happen.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.DoMouseLeave
Summary
  Called in response to a mouse leave message.
Description
  DoMouseLeave is called whenever the mouse leave message is received. If OnMouseLeave is assigned
  it will be called, otherwise nothing will happen.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.DoParentColorChange
Summary
  Called in response to the parent color change message.
Description
  DoParentColor is called whenever the parent color change message is received. If
  OnParentColorChange is assigned, it will be called, otherwise nothing will happen.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the hint box.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. A default color value of clInfoBk is set for the
  HintColor property in the constructor of the control. To change the HintColor assign it a new
  TColor value.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.OnMouseEnter
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves over the control.
Description
  Write an OnMouseEnter event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse over the
  control.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the control.
Description
  Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  control.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAnimate.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color of the parent control changes.
Description
  Write an OnParentColorChange event handler to take specific action when the parent's Color
  property changes.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

